title: Rodney Dinkles
description:
Join us for the Dirty Not Sorry Bergerac Residency featuring special headliner Rodney Dinkles

One of DJ Mag’s top 10 emerging artists, LA based DJ/Producer Rodney Dinkles is a recent graduate of Just Justin Jay’s music production school. RD already made his debut on Dirtybird Records with “Welcome Dance”, plus a mix featured on Dirtybird Radio. In only two years, Rodney has amassed a massive discography including 40 tracks signed to Fantastic Voyage, Artichokes Are Yellow, House of Hustle, Colapso, Music is 4 Lovers, and his very own label imprint: Qwerk. Keep an eye out for his forthcoming release on Shiba San’s Basement Leak, and other labels including his new Justin Jay collab.
